OL,6,FA memorial service has been held for a
OL,7,F15-year old boy who died after getting
OL,8,Finto difficulty in the water at
OL,9,FAberavon beach in Port Talbot a year
OL,10,Fago.
OL,12,FDavid Ejimofor was celebrating the end
OL,13,Fof his GCSEs.
OL,15,FDavid's mum Maria said "David was an
OL,16,Fincredible person, very kind,
OL,17,Fgenerous, fun and cheeky. If he was
OL,18,Fhere now he'd be like 'look at
OL,19,Feveryone here now just for me'
