OL,6,F"I don't come to the beach now. This
OL,7,Fwas my first time of coming, just to
OL,8,Fremember him and with the plaque as
OL,9,Fwell, because every time I come here
OL,10,Fit's too painful.
OL,12,F"Losing your child is like a death
OL,13,Fsentence."
OL,15,F"We will keep David in our hearts and
OL,16,Fkeep moving and keep David's legacy
OL,17,Fgoing, because David would want us to
OL,18,Fbe alive to carry him with us, and
OL,19,Fthat's what keeps us going."
