OL,6,FAssociated British Ports told ITV
OL,7,FWales:J"As the inquest has not yet
OL,8,Fbeen held, it is not appropriate for
OL,9,FAssociated British Ports to comment on
OL,10,Fany specific aspects of the incident.
OL,11,FHowever, our deepest sympathy and
OL,12,Fthoughts remain with David's family
OL,13,Fand friends and all who knew him."
OL,15,F"We continue to work with local
OL,16,Fstakeholders and partners regarding
OL,17,Fwater safety at Port Talbot."
